title: MUGCLUB EXCLUSIVE: Crowder on Firearm Open Carry, Getting Started on YouTube & Police Sketch of Michael Jackson!
description: In this MugClub exclusive compilation, Crowder and crew give Manny the Police Sketch Artist clues to draw Michael Jackson. Later, Crowder discusses getting started on YouTube, his inspiration from Andrew Breitbart, and why he supports open carry of firearms.
